    "content": "<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Stunning Pagination Design</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3f4f6, #e5e7eb);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            height: 100vh;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            background: white;\n            animation: slideIn 1s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes slideIn {\n            from {\n                transform: translateY(-100%);\n                opacity: 0;\n            }\n            to {\n                transform: translateY(0);\n                opacity: 1;\n            }\n        }\n\n        .header {\n            background: #4F46E5;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .content {\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n\n        .pagination {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background: #e0e7ff;\n        }\n\n        .page-button {\n            margin: 0 10px;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            background: #4F46E5;\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .page-button:hover {\n            background: #3B3E99;\n        }\n\n        .disabled {\n            background: #d1d5db;\n            cursor: not-allowed;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">Welcome to Stunning Pagination</div>\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <p>This is the most visually appealing pagination example you will ever encounter. Pause and enjoy the aesthetics.</p>\n            <p>Each page gracefully transitions with a subtle animation adding to the immersive experience.</p>\n            <p>Pages are designed with readability and elegance in mind, ensuring that users can focus on the content without distractions.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pagination\">\n            <button class=\"page-button\" onclick=\"previousPage()\">Previous</button>\n            <button class=\"page-button\" onclick=\"nextPage()\">Next</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        let currentPage = 1;\n        const totalPages = 5;\n\n        function previousPage() {\n            if (currentPage > 1) {\n                currentPage--;\n                updateContent();\n            }\n        }\n\n        function nextPage() {\n            if (currentPage < totalPages) {\n                currentPage++;\n                updateContent();\n            }\n        }\n\n        function updateContent() {\n            const content = document.querySelector('.content');\n            content.innerHTML = `<p>Welcome to page ${currentPage}. This is an example of a stunning design.</p>\n                                <p>Page ${currentPage} of ${totalPages}.</p>`;\n        }\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
